    <div id="header" style="margin-top:10px;">
        <h1>Vocal coaching and accompaniment</h1>
        <img width="413" height="310" align="right" alt="Vocal coaching and accompaniment" title="Vocal coaching and accompaniment" src="/images/vocal_coaching_and_accompaniment.jpg" style="margin-left: 11px; border:2px solid #FFF"/>
        <div class="bodytext">
            <p>Anastasiya provides vocal coaching, giving singers the opportunity to work with an experienced pianist and offering them the chance to test their repertoire with the piano, a must for anyone preparing for live performances.</p>
            <p>With the empathic nature of Anastasiya's art of piano playing, she endeavours with her sensitive, colourful and imaginative accompaniment to bring out the best from the singer. As a result, this helps to free the voice, improve the singer's ensemble working skills and ultimately, increases the vocalist's performing confidence.</p>
            <div style="float: right; margin: 11px; width:365px; text-align: center;">
                <iframe style="width:335px; height:234px;"  src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/l5Ube9-u3Sc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                <br/><span style="color: #444444; line-height: 17px; font-size:13px; ">Lo, Here the Gentle Lark! H. R. Bishop with Donna Galagher</span>
            </div>
            <p>Anastasiya has worked with singers from Ireland, Czech Republic and Ukraine, and has accompanied opera singers in numerous concerts in the Czech Republic, Germany, Brazil, Ukraine and Ireland. She has worked as an accompanist for Opera Ireland and has performed with singers in the National Concert Hall. She has also coached and accompanied numerous Feis Ceoil competitors.</p>

            <div style="float: right; margin: 11px; width:365px; text-align: center;">
                <iframe style="width:335px; height:234px;"  src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/-W_aY-n7FRE" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                <br/><span style="color: #444444; line-height: 17px; font-size:13px; ">My Lagan Love with Michael Lang</span>
            </div>
            <p>Anastasiya has an extensive range of linguistic skills, having fluency in Russian, English, Czech and Italian. This can be most advantageous to those singers working with material in these languages.</p>

            <div style="float: right; margin: 11px; width:365px; text-align: center;">
                <iframe style="width:335px; height:234px;"  src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/46ViIlX2wwo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                <br/><span style="color: #444444; line-height: 17px; font-size:13px; ">Ave Maria by Caccini with Sinead Grogan</span>
            </div>

            <p>Anastasiya also plays chamber music and can offer her services to those musicians who are looking for an accompanist, whether it be for concerts, exams, auditions or other events.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
